# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Description
#   Configuration file for Readline.
#   Full documentation on inputrc is available with: 
#     $ info rluserman
#   To see current bindings, run:
#     $ bind -p
#
# Author
#   nicoulaj - http://www.ju-n.net
